subject: Hello Carlos
body:
How are you doing today.
Am contacting you concerning your fund which has in our custody, I wait
to hear from you for immediate procedure of your fund Ok.

subject: Re: Hello Carlos
body:
Hello! I'm doing well, thank you for asking. I appreciate you reaching out to me about my fund. Can you please provide me with more details about it? I would like to understand the procedure and how I can access it.

Best wishes,
Carlos

subject: Re: Hello Carlos
body:
This is a compensation fund from United State government for scam victims.
You have to send me your address if you need it delivered to you but if you
want it transferred into your bank account then send me your
account details.
I'm waiting to hear from you soon okay

body:
